= SDL_GetNumDisplayModes =
Use this function to return the number of available display modes for the current display.


== Syntax ==
```c++
int SDL_GetNumDisplayModes(void)
```

== Return Value ==
Returns a number >= 1 on success or a negative error code on failure; call [[SDL_GetError]]() for more information.

